### Get all employees
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees

### EMPLOYEE TASKS

### Employee 1 - Create vacation request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/vacation-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vacationStartDate": "2025-12-25",
  "vacationEndDate": "2025-12-30",
  "reason": "Christmas vacation"
}

### Employee 2 - Create vacation request  
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees/2/vacation-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vacationStartDate": "2025-12-20",
  "vacationEndDate": "2025-12-24",
  "reason": "Holiday break"
}

### Employee 3 - Create vacation request (overlapping)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees/3/vacation-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vacationStartDate": "2025-12-23",
  "vacationEndDate": "2025-12-27",
  "reason": "Year end vacation"
}

### Employee 1 - View their vacation requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/vacation-requests

### Employee 1 - View their vacation requests filtered by status (pending)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/vacation-requests?status=pending

### Employee 1 - View their vacation requests filtered by status (approved)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/vacation-requests?status=approved

### Employee 1 - View vacation summary (remaining days)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1/vacation-summary

### Employee 2 - View vacation summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/2/vacation-summary

### MANAGER TASKS

### Manager 4 - View all vacation requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/vacation-requests

### Manager 4 - View pending requests only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/vacation-requests?status=pending

### Manager 4 - View approved requests only  
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/vacation-requests?status=approved

### Manager 4 - View pending and approved requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/vacation-requests?status=pending,approved

### Manager 4 - View specific employee's requests (Employee 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/employees/1/vacation-requests

### Manager 4 - View specific employee's requests (Employee 2)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/employees/2/vacation-requests

### Manager 4 - View overlapping requests for date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/overlapping-requests?startDate=2025-12-20&endDate=2025-12-30

### Manager 4 - Approve vacation request 
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/vacation-requests/1?action=approve

### Manager 4 - Reject vacation request 
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/managers/4/vacation-requests/2?action=reject

### Manager 5 - Approve vacation request 
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/managers/5/vacation-requests/3?action=approve

